      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p>This bill amends the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act to preempt state laws that establish squatter\u2019s rights for premises owned by a servicemember in situations where the premises is occupied by a squatter during a period of military service of the servicemember.</p>",
